Arioch is a noble+baatezu serving as Dispater's avenger, meting out punishment upon all on Dis who fail or otherwise displease his master, and serving as Dispater's bodyguard.
His flat, crocodilian head is ringed with a leonine mane. His skin is dark wine-red, deepening to purple on his head and shoulders and on his great, bat-like wings. Arioch has a forked tail, great cloven hooves, and heavily muscled arms.
Source: Dragon #75, Fiendish Codex II